description.plain: Featuring members of acclaimed acts such as Elvenking and Secret Sphere, HELL IN THE CLUB have clearly earned their place in the scene but their music stands out as something totally different: they mix classic hard rock and modern sounds, heavy metal and party songs, fifties rock’n’roll and anything in between.
